  "time_ut": 1657529157,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dcf \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Attack on media condemns burning of Prime Minister's house\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Karu Jayasuriya, Chairman of the National Movement for a Fair Society, says that Sirasa strongly condemns the attack on a group of journalists and the burning of the Prime Minister's private house.",
        "Mr. Jayasuriya also stated in a statement that both these incidents are serious and sustainable acts that are despised by the civilized society, and those responsible should be punished in front of the law regardless of their rank.",
        "The announcement issued by former speaker Mr. Karu Jayasuriya, Chairman of the National Movement for a Fair Society further states:",
        "\"We are extremely shocked by two brutal incidents that we heard during the massive struggle that the people of the country were carrying out for the sake of democracy and freedom of the people.",
        "The two incidents are the attack by a group of officers of the Police Special Task Force on a media group, including a journalist from Sirasa Media Institute, who was carrying out its duties for the people's right to know information, and the destruction of the Prime Minister's private house by a group of people.",
        "Both these incidents are serious and sustainable acts that are abhorred by civilized society. We strongly condemn both incidents. We also emphasize that those responsible should be punished before the law regardless of their rank. It is important that the heads of the Police Special Task Force act immediately and take disciplinary action against the concerned officers.",
        "In order to find a solution to the massive political and economic as well as social crisis in the country today, it is extremely important to educate the public about it. The role of the media is huge. We wish a speedy recovery to the group of journalists who are currently undergoing treatment and we thank Sirasa Media and the entire media community for the work they are doing.",
        "We also strongly condemn the burning of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's private house. Dissent should have the highest respect in democratic politics. A society that does not accept the right to hold a different political opinion cannot have a good future. In the name of the future generation of the country, we as a society must take care not to create such situations in the future. We expect that the attention of the entire society of the country will be focused on that. It is also important to find out if there are hidden forces behind this event.",
        "Our sole objective is to see the country recover. It should be respectfully pointed out that Parliament as well as the entire society has a national responsibility."
      ],
